{
  "id": 5172818344148992,
  "name": "Playback Statistics API for WebAudio",
  "summary": "This feature adds an AudioContext.playbackStats attribute which returns an AudioPlaybackStats object. This object provides audio playback statistics such as average latency, minimum/maximum latency, underrun duration, and underrun count. This API allows web applications to monitor audio playback quality and detect glitches.\n\nNote: This feature was previously tracked as AudioContext.playoutStats. It has been renamed to AudioContext.playbackStats to align with the final Web Audio API specification. The old name is supported as a deprecated alias for backward compatibility.",
