          "ot_require_approvals": false,
          "ot_use_counter_bucket_number": null,
          "ot_webfeature_use_counter": null,
          "extensions": [],
          "experiment_extension_reason": "We need additional time to work with Privacy WG to address their concerns.\n\nSince the origin trial started, we have made the following progress:\n* The API was presented at TPAC, and got a positive reaction from Audio WG. However, they wanted to hear the Privacy WG's input, and that we should ask the internal privacy/security reviewers why the API is ok while the similar RenderCapacity API was not ok. ( https://docs.google.com/document/d/1QiBmVZb51ATyai_TTbkMnq25zaQOzVNxNIsPJZ8sdUE/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.el9c5z4prh05 )\n* We have presented the API to the Privacy WG and they have discussed it (https://github.com/w3c/privacywg/blob/main/minutes/privacywg-20250417.md#webaudio) . We are now having an active discussion with them about how we can address their concerns.\n* Google-internal privacy/security reviewers have reaffirmed that the API is ok, and safer than the RenderCapacity API.\n* We have added wpt tests for the API.",
          "ot_stage_id": 5075398620872704,
          "finch_url": null,
