          "ot_webfeature_use_counter": null,
          "extensions": [],
          "experiment_extension_reason": "Since the previous extension, we have presented the API to the Audio WG, where it was agreed that we should land the API in the WebAudio spec. The PR[1] has had a number of rounds of review, and is now close to landing (as discussed at TPAC 2025) [2].\n\nSince the requested changes to the API include naming changes, applications using the Origin Trial version of the API will not be compatible with the new version of the API out of the box. To give us time to land the spec and to give applications time to migrate to the new version, we are requesting an extension of 3 milestones until 145.\n\n[1] https://github.com/WebAudio/web-audio-api/pull/2645 \n[2] https://docs.google.com/document/d/15bLL2UujSW4OdSa0Kv66wziXBTq34jWOntNDbs2pPek/edit?tab=t.dpp97ymwtdhx#heading=h.m9ld885gturz ",
